title: Can Jeremy Corbyn's red army of virgin voters sweep him to No 10?
text: Jeremy Corbyn Can Jeremy Corbyn's red army of virgin voters sweep him to No 10? Labour's leader has insisted that new voters, not existing ones, are the route to power. Could he actually be right? Jeremy Corbyn arrives at the special conference held to announce the results of the Labour leadership contest Photo: Rex
